Interface Group

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Accessible, Accessor, Entity, Identifiable, ItemHolder, Named, PermissionGrantTarget, PermissionScope, com.tinkerpop.frames.VertexFrame
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Group.Impl

    public interface Group
extends Accessor, Accessible, PermissionScope, Named, ItemHolder
    Frame class representing a group of users or other groups that can be assigned permissions.
